  <heading>UZPQ2</heading>
  <desc>
    <brief>
      <para>Concatenate odd elements within each pair of quadword vector segments</para>
    </brief>
    <authored>
      <para>This instruction concatenates adjacent odd-numbered elements from the corresponding
128-bit vector segments of the first and second source vectors and
places in elements of the corresponding destination vector segment.
This instruction is unpredicated.</para>
    </authored>
    <predicated>False</predicated>
    <uses_dit condition="FEAT_SVE2 is implemented or FEAT_SME is implemented">True</uses_dit>
  </desc>
